<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Accessibility | Glass City Trailer Rentals</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Glass City Trailer Rentals' accessibility statement and commitment to WCAG 2.1 AA." />
  <link rel="icon" href="/images/logo.png" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Anton&family=DM+Sans:opsz,wght@9..40,300;9..40,400;9..40,500;9..40,600;9..40,700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/site.css" />
  <style>
    .doc { max-width: 720px; margin: 44px auto 80px; }
    .doc h2 { font-family: 'Anton', sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 22px; margin: 28px 0 10px; }
    .doc p, .doc li { color: #cfd3c9; line-height: 1.7; }
    .doc ul { padding-left: 20px; }
    .doc a { color: var(--green); text-decoration: underline; }
    .updated { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: var(--ink-dim); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .1em; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <a class="skip-link" href="#main">Skip to content</a>
  <header class="site-head">
    <div class="site-head-inner">
      <a class="back" href="/">‹ <span>Home</span></a>
      <a href="/"><img class="logo" src="/images/logo.png" alt="Glass City Trailer Rentals" /></a>
      <a class="call" href="tel:+14196543584" aria-label="Call Glass City Trailer Rentals">Call</a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="container" id="main">
    <div class="doc">
      <div class="eyebrow">Accessibility</div>
      <h1 class="display" style="font-size:clamp(34px,6vw,56px);margin:8px 0 6px;">Accessibility Statement</h1>
      <p class="updated">Last updated <%= updated %></p>

      <p>
        Glass City Trailer Rentals LLC is committed to making our website usable by
        everyone, including people who rely on assistive technology. We aim to meet the
        <strong>Web Content Accessibility Guidelines (WCAG) 2.1, Level AA</strong>.
      </p>

      <h2>What we do</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Semantic structure with landmarks, headings, and a skip-to-content link.</li>
        <li>Labels and clear error messages on every form field.</li>
        <li>Full keyboard operability with visible focus indicators.</li>
        <li>Color contrast that meets the AA threshold, and respect for reduced-motion preferences.</li>
        <li>Text alternatives for images and informative graphics.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>No accessibility overlays</h2>
      <p>
        We do <strong>not</strong> use third-party accessibility “overlay” or “widget”
        plugins. Accessibility is built into the site itself, not bolted on by a script.
      </p>

      <h2>Need help, or found a problem?</h2>
      <p>
        If any part of this site is hard to use, or you need information in another format,
        please tell us and we’ll help directly and fix the issue:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Phone: <a href="tel:+14196543584">(419) 654-3584</a></li>
        <li>Email: <a href="mailto:glasscitytrailerrentals@gmail.com?subject=Accessibility%20issue">glasscitytrailerrentals@gmail.com</a></li>
        <li>In person: 2004 Front Street, Toledo, OH 43605</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We aim to respond within two business days.</p>

      <p style="margin-top:28px;"><a href="/">← Back to home</a></p>
    </div>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
